Notes (Uncategorized):
Following practice for other 760-787 linking fields for Phase I, per Ebe Kartus, with some changes to reflect additional fields and omitted fields for this tag.

MARCSubfield: a, b, d, g, h, i, k, l, m, n, o, p, q, r, s,t, u, w, x, y, z, 3, 4, 5
Justification for Mapping: If $5 is present, generate item IRI and treat note as note on item (see $5 mapping)
Transformation Notes:
Mint an IRI for an item, associate it with the manifestation using rdamo:P30103, then apply this property for all subfields as described in "has note on manifestation" mapping, (along with mapping the same item to a collection as indicated for subfield 5).
LNA 2025-2-28
Problems with Mapping: Association of the note string with its "authoring institution" is indirect (the institution is associated with the same minted item IRI).

Notes (Uncategorized): Content of $6 (tag and numbering of tag in relation to others) not mapped, only used for relating fields containing the subfield.  --LNA 2/16/2025
